Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.68,0:00:10.27,Italics,Goblin Slayer,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a child, I thought I'd become \Nan adventurer when I grew up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.73,0:00:14.48,Italics,Gs,0000,0000,0000,,I'd leave my village and defeat the evil \Nmonsters that were tormenting the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.99,0:00:25.38,Italics,Gs,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I'd become powerful \Nenough to defeat even dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.14,0:00:29.54,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'd become a hero, \Na platinum-ranked adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.54,0:00:32.16,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,O-Once this is over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.16,0:00:35.63,Main,Hero,0000,0000,0000,,the three of us are going back to \Nthe village and going to a festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.19,Main,Swordmaster,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's in the same boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.19,0:00:42.01,Main,Swordmaster,0000,0000,0000,,We all have someone dear to us\Nand things we want to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.17,0:00:45.51,Main,Sage,0000,0000,0000,,To ensure that even small \Nwishes like that come true...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.64,0:00:48.66,Main,SA,0000,0000,0000,,We can't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.64,0:00:54.16,Main,H,0000,0000,0000,,We have to save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.67,0:00:59.48,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I couldn't become a hero...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.03,0:01:08.46,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd be able to \Nbecome an adventurer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.45,0:01:16.76,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,If only I were able to leave my older sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:19.38,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,who had raised me all on her own, behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:52.76,Flashback,Cow girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to the city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.76,0:02:56.47,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go to my uncle's farm and \Nhelp one of the cows give birth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.04,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,And once I'm done helping,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.04,0:03:03.73,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I can go shopping in the city.\NMy mom gave me some money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:06.18,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what I should buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.18,0:03:09.10,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything you want? \NI'll buy you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.14,Flashback,GS,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.56,0:03:13.46,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,There must be something. I mean—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.38,Flashback,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't want anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:18.04,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you have to say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.29,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to buy you something \Nsince you've never been to the city...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:27.34,Flashback,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Just go to the city or wherever!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.75,0:03:29.03,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you getting mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.03,0:03:30.23,Flashback,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.51,Flashback,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:36.47,Flashback,Older Sister,0000,0000,0000,,You must've been envious \Nthat she was going to the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.93,0:03:40.08,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you shouldn't have acted like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.81,0:03:43.12,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,You have to protect girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.07,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.47,0:03:49.53,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,that if you envy others, you become a goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:50.90,Flashback,GS,0000,0000,0000,,A goblin?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:55.22,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. If all you ever do is dwell \Non the things you don't have,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.22,0:03:58.02,Flashback,Os,0000,0000,0000,,your heart and body warp \Ninto something unsightly,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.02,0:04:00.37,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,and you start trying to take \Nthings from others by force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:03.48,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,So, later on,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.48,0:04:05.85,Flashback,OS,0000,0000,0000,,let's make sure you apologize to her, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:13.68,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,That night, my sister made my favorite \Nstew with chicken and milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.02,0:04:22.80,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,It was so delicious, I ate bowl after bowl,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.62,0:04:26.37,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,but now I can't even remember \Nhow that stew tasted.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.41,0:04:30.49,Italics,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:45.75,Italics,Gs,0000,0000,0000,,it's because I haven't \Neaten it since that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:50.71,Ep_Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(276,1)}Dozing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:08.27,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.59,0:05:10.47,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.86,0:05:14.10,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like today's going to be a hot one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.22,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's no surprise. \NIt's summer, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.49,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:21.33,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:24.57,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I think my uncle is awake, \Nso let's have breakfast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:25.83,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:32.30,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.30,0:05:35.08,Main,Uncle,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. Were you doing your usual patrols?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.08,0:05:38.08,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir. There were no issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.08,0:05:41.04,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,I really don't think you \Nneed to worry so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.66,0:05:44.39,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Demon Lord \Nwas defeated by the Hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.04,0:05:46.97,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the monsters will calm down a—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:47.65,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:51.40,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,At least, goblins won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.40,0:05:53.34,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.34,0:05:54.01,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:57.99,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry. It took a little \Nlonger than I thought it would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.99,0:06:00.81,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lay everything out now, so let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.12,0:06:05.09,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,After breakfast, I have \Nto go make deliveries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:07.96,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go, too. I have to stop by the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:10.17,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's go together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.59,0:06:15.34,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to the city to accept a quest?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.87,0:06:19.44,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,That, too, but I also need to get my gear \Nrepaired and pick up my other set of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:21.16,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.44,0:06:28.85,Main,U,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything rash. \NI don't want to see her hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.43,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.41,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,You need to stop by the guild, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.41,0:06:39.26,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.26,0:06:42.85,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,After I'm done with my deliveries, \Nthere's something I want to buy,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.85,0:06:46.39,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,so let's meet up later to head home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.39,0:06:47.41,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:52.91,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:55.86,Main,Spearman,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are pasty for \Nsomeone who's so ripped.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.53,0:06:58.51,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen you around before. You new?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.51,0:06:59.43,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.63,0:07:02.62,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,So... you're just dropping in \Non a day off or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.62,0:07:03.99,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.51,0:07:08.50,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, if you actually wanted to make \Nmoney as an adventurer right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.80,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,you'd go to the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.80,0:07:13.61,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,A lot of the Demon Lord's army is still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.61,0:07:17.03,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,They're just stragglers, so they'd be \Neasy to take care of for good pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.29,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.29,0:07:21.79,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Me? You can't be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.61,0:07:27.71,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Bullying the weak isn't my style.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.03,0:07:30.49,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,I only fight for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.49,0:07:32.79,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got no interest in money or peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:34.00,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.13,Main,Guild Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:38.42,Main,Guild Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I'll listen to all of your concerns, \Nso form a single file line, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.42,0:07:41.97,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:45.52,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, I have no need for catchy slogans.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.96,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.96,0:07:48.50,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:53.77,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, see ya. I've got some \Nruins that need exploring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:55.40,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,Wish me luck in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.40,0:07:56.40,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I shall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.31,0:07:59.21,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,The stoic type, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.21,0:08:01.53,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind that, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.87,0:08:04.16,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any... quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.62,0:08:05.83,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.57,0:08:09.79,Main,Smith,0000,0000,0000,,I had some extra time, \Nso I fixed the smaller bits, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.25,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,How's it feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:20.72,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.72,0:08:22.93,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,And now to repair this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.83,0:08:25.01,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,For crying out loud...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.22,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,How'd your armor get so damaged \Njust from fighting goblins?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:30.79,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Were you able to get me a scroll?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:34.22,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Those things are hard to come by.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:36.13,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Keep yer shirt on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:37.14,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.78,0:08:45.20,Main,Apprentice Boy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, boss. That guy's a \Nsilver-ranked adventurer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.53,0:08:47.85,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's what I've heard, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.85,0:08:49.76,Main,AB,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he wear all that armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.18,0:08:53.58,Main,AB,0000,0000,0000,,If he wanted to be quieter, \Nwouldn't mithril chainmail be better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.15,0:08:56.19,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.90,Main,AB,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I do... I mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:01.51,Main,AB,0000,0000,0000,,he'd be better off with a \Nmagical sword than a scroll...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.70,0:09:07.80,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,Only a munchkin would wave around a \Nlegendary magical sword at some goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.80,0:09:12.27,Main,S,0000,0000,0000,,He knows exactly what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.93,Main,Young Scout,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:19.60,Main,Heavy Swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, what's the matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:21.86,Main,Heavy Swordsman,0000,0000,0000,,You won't even be able to \Nkill goblins at that rate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:25.94,Main,Greenhorn Warrior,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! We're going for the opening!\N Go around the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.94,0:09:27.07,Main,YS,0000,0000,0000,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:28.95,Main,Rhea Druid,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds like a great plan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:30.70,Main,Apprentice Cleric,0000,0000,0000,,You probably shouldn't say it out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.71,0:09:34.78,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,You're too naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:38.54,Main,Female Knight,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey, Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.49,0:09:42.59,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you almost died in Water Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:43.79,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.79,0:09:47.38,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, are you always dressed like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:48.26,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.26,0:09:49.23,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:53.96,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that warrior \Nwas part of your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:57.49,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... We were sparring with our little brat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:59.61,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,and we saw him staring the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.56,0:10:04.20,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer's skill with the \Nsword is mostly self-taught.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:08.36,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,If you learn actual swordsmanship at least \Nonce, you'll have a chance to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.93,0:10:09.49,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:14.58,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,I need to teach those girls \Na bit about survival, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:19.02,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that giant ball of energy \Nis starting to lose his breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.59,0:10:22.09,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll join in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.82,0:10:24.42,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,Have at you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.95,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,You're always bragging \Nabout how mighty you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.95,0:10:29.84,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm sure you'd consider this fair game.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.84,0:10:33.38,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,What?! And you call yourself \Na paladin candidate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:35.42,Main,FK,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.42,0:10:38.00,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't effective training for anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.73,0:10:39.77,Main,YS,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.77,0:10:40.90,Main,GHW,0000,0000,0000,,We're saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.98,0:10:43.98,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,You sure aren't holding back, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.18,0:11:00.74,Main,Priestess,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.34,0:11:02.90,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.90,0:11:05.23,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My armor needed some repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.23,0:11:07.47,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You should've said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.47,0:11:08.80,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really need to.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.51,0:11:11.76,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,How's your shoulder doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:16.02,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? O-Oh, it's fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.02,0:11:18.85,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,They cast a healing spell on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.85,0:11:19.79,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:20.51,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:25.49,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Goblin Slayer. How'd the \Nquest at Water Town go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.51,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,It's been taken care of. \NThere weren't any problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:31.53,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?! You almost died!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.53,0:11:34.28,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,What?! A-Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:36.12,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.12,0:11:38.40,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have your wounds properly tended to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:40.04,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.02,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.02,0:11:50.37,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,N-No. Nothing at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.43,0:11:54.27,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,What did you need?\N Do you have a quest for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.27,0:11:56.39,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,No, not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.19,0:12:03.10,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,An adventurer from Water Town asked \Nme to give this letter to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.10,0:12:04.66,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:09.22,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,No problem. It's part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.92,0:12:12.79,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have an acquaintance in Water Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.53,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.91,0:12:15.96,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably from the one \Nwho requested the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.96,0:12:18.42,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that makes sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:20.72,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,The one who requested the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:25.75,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,The Sword Maiden wrote \NGoblin Slayer a letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.54,0:12:27.68,Italics,P,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:32.34,Main,Dwarf Shaman,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if it isn't Beard-cutter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:36.18,Main,High Elf Archer,0000,0000,0000,,You should've at least come to \Nsay hi if you were here, Orcbolg!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.18,0:12:40.47,Main,Lizardman Priest,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's a relief that your armor seems to \Nhave been repaired, Sir Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.28,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:45.36,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to go get some food. \NWant to join us, Beard-cutter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:47.27,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,You should come, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:48.45,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.45,0:12:50.19,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, uh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.10,0:12:52.95,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:54.39,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.39,0:12:56.72,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.72,0:12:58.31,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:00.87,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Let's go, Orcbolg.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:03.11,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.04,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:08.13,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,My, you've got a lot of friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.38,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.83,0:13:12.18,Main,Inspector,0000,0000,0000,,How amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.09,0:13:17.35,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, if you were waiting for someone, \Nyou should've just told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.73,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who forced \NBeard-cutter to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.73,0:13:24.60,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I didn't know, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.41,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Um, is it really okay \Nfor me to join you all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.41,0:13:29.52,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.94,0:13:32.99,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,Please, help yourself, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:36.74,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Food always tastes better \Nwhen you eat in a big group.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.59,0:13:39.45,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'll dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.23,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,This is great, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.90,0:13:52.67,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is the rumor that the Hero \Ndefeated the Demon Lord true?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:57.30,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is! We've received \Nword from the capital.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.55,0:14:03.83,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the Hero became the tenth \Nplatinum-ranked adventurer in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:08.52,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,That's splendid. Now we can all rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:12.11,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's quite a celebration \Ngoing on in the capital right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:14.60,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we should start celebrating ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.81,0:14:18.33,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Like you need an excuse to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.33,0:14:21.92,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez... Maybe I should've \Ngone to the capital, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.92,0:14:26.77,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as big as the one in the capital, \Nbut we also have a harvest festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.30,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,A harvest festival, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.72,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,Join me for a drink, Beard-cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.67,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm going to pass today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.07,0:14:35.26,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Why not have a taste of this, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:39.57,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, it's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.57,0:14:40.71,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.20,0:14:45.60,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,It has lemon and honey in it. \NApparently it helps with fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:50.18,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Maybe I should consider carrying \Nsome with me on my adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:53.73,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,Now that training's over, it's time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:57.46,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,It's all on me! Eat up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.86,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the grub!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:02.02,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like they've been training all morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:04.62,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,Applying oneself to one's craft is a fine thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.33,0:15:10.83,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,There have been talks recently \Nabout opening up a training hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.88,0:15:14.34,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,They want to hire retired adventurers.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:18.18,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many newcomers \Nwho really don't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:19.62,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:23.72,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,The more they know, the more \Nlikely they are to come back alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.72,0:15:25.52,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,It'll give them confidence, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.79,0:15:28.36,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention that even \Nwhen adventurers retire,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:30.55,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,they'll continue to live until they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.55,0:15:33.15,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,So I think it's beneficial to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.47,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:38.47,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,So you need to be more \Ncareful, Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.11,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:42.57,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I won't give you any more quests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:46.29,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,The next time you collapse, \Nno more adventures for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.29,0:15:48.16,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. No adventuring allowed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.75,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,That would be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.17,0:15:52.21,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:55.30,Main,GG,0000,0000,0000,,So make sure you take \Nbetter care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.75,0:16:00.80,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,All your friends are such nice people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.80,0:16:01.79,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:04.25,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,"Are they"? You mean they aren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.58,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,They're skilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:09.68,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I have a higher probability of \Ncrushing goblins if I'm in a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.09,0:16:12.31,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.59,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:17.14,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.14,0:16:18.11,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:19.42,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:21.58,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:38.34,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Goblin Slayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:41.72,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,How are you doing in these hard times,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.72,0:16:45.01,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,where the fire spirit continues its dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.77,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,Under normal circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:51.94,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,I would have sent a letter \Nof gratitude much sooner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.89,0:16:56.61,Italics,Sm,0000,0000,0000,,but I told myself that \NI shouldn't trouble you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.57,0:16:59.36,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:03.76,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,By some miracle, ever since that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.76,0:17:06.18,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,the goblins have stopped \Nplaguing my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:08.26,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,and I've been living peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:13.25,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,This is all thanks to you and your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:16.11,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.02,0:17:19.37,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon Lord has been \Ndefeated by the Hero,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.37,0:17:22.25,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,which should lead the world toward peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.88,0:17:25.15,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,But many of the Demon \NLord's army still remain,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.15,0:17:28.01,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,so we mustn't let down our guard yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:33.87,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that the adventurers \Nwill have to continue their fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:39.18,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,but I am always praying for your safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.64,0:17:43.95,Italics,SM,0000,0000,0000,,Sincerely, the Sword Maiden. Sending prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:50.10,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh! You're so loud, and you \Nnever know when to quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.10,0:17:53.00,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! I've had enough! \NLet's finish this, dwarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.77,0:17:58.38,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some guts, long-ears. \NDon't worry, I'll go easy on ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.04,0:18:01.95,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna have my fire wine, \Nand you can have regular ol' wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:02.76,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,What do ya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:05.09,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.48,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:10.10,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,The wise never court danger, milady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.52,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me more!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.32,0:18:16.09,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Pour me another!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:17.21,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.15,0:18:25.36,Main,SP,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? Looks like you're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:27.76,Main,Witch,0000,0000,0000,,Place some... bets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.76,0:18:32.25,Main,FM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting on the girl. Three gold pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:35.37,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,Well, aren't you confident? \NYou sure you can afford that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.45,Main,FM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going for the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:41.21,Main,FM,0000,0000,0000,,I'm disciplined, righteous, and have \Nthe protection of the gods.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:45.63,Main,HS,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't the Supreme God be against gambling?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.63,0:18:47.49,Main,YS,0000,0000,0000,,I'm betting on the dwarf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.32,Main,GW,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm betting on the elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.22,Main,AC,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That's all of our earnings from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.88,0:18:55.09,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Are you sure we shouldn't stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:58.66,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,It won't take many more drinks \Nbefore Sir Mage wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.66,0:19:00.52,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,Or so I'd like to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.64,Main,Lp,0000,0000,0000,,but Lady Ranger is also stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.64,0:19:04.37,Main,LP,0000,0000,0000,,There's just no way to tell yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.37,0:19:06.24,Main,P,0000,0000,0000,,You say that like this isn't our problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.16,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,Next! I'm nowhere near done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.38,0:19:10.41,Main,DS,0000,0000,0000,,Drink up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.06,0:19:17.95,Main,HEA,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.20,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.58,0:19:38.47,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I came to tell you that dinner's ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.06,0:19:43.40,Main,Cg,0000,0000,0000,,and I wanted to know what \Nyou were thinking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:45.82,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,About the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:47.50,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,The future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.42,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.49,0:19:50.66,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:53.70,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.70,0:19:55.00,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:58.64,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing. Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.24,0:20:02.42,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,You're strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.68,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get grease all over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.68,0:20:13.72,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:16.72,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to do laundry, anyway. \NAnd I'll take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.19,0:20:18.40,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.51,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.86,0:20:27.57,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our time, you know, \Nthinking about the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:29.05,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Take our time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.86,Main,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. There's no need to rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.25,Main,GS,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.62,0:20:46.96,Italics,Cg,0000,0000,0000,,The future, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.46,0:20:49.94,Flashback,GG,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention that even \Nwhen adventurers retire,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.16,Flashback,GG,0000,0000,0000,,they'll continue to live until they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:54.43,Flashback,GG,0000,0000,0000,,So I think it's beneficial to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.50,0:20:58.43,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,People get old and get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.39,0:21:02.98,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,When they're tired, they collapse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.94,0:21:09.57,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, everyone reaches their limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:16.45,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,whether it be an adventurer or a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.73,0:21:20.86,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he doesn't die,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.86,0:21:25.25,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,there'll come a day when he'll \Nno longer be able to slay goblins.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.90,0:21:29.33,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,These days won't last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.70,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,And when that day comes, what can he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.31,0:21:36.13,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,What should he do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.22,0:21:40.29,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't have the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:45.48,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, no one has the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.49,0:22:05.75,Italics,CG,0000,0000,0000,,No one has the answer.